welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Moose Jaw, Canada! Get ready to experience the charming small-town vibe and discover our city's rich history as a hub for mining and agriculture. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Moose Jaw has to offer."

airports.airport_name: Moose Jaw / Air Vice Marshal C. M. Mcewen Airport

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Moose Jaw / Air Vice Marshal C. M. Mcewen Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Moose Jaw / Air Vice Marshal C. M. Mcewen Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport terminal.
